    <item>
      <title>About</title>
      <link>https://sarthak93.github.io/blog/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2014 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sarthak93.github.io/blog/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hey there! I am Sarthak Jain, final year student from IIT Kharagpur. As of now I&amp;rsquo;m majoring in Civil Engineering, with specialisation in structures.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Keeping up with the open source world, I managed to bring this blog site up using &lt;a href=&#34;http://gohugo.io/&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://pages.github.com&#34;&gt;GitHub Pages&lt;/a&gt; which I found to be pretty cool and easy.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My main motive is to share my views, thoughts and activities I keeep doing as an engineer in the making.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Have questions or suggestions? Feel free to &lt;a href=&#34;http://sarthakjain.info&#34;&gt;contact me&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reading!&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Contact</title>
